sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant Feed as Feed Service
    participant Rec as Recommendation Service
    participant ANN as Vector Store (ANN)
    participant Rank as Ranking Model
    participant DB as Metadata Store
    participant Ev as Interaction Stream

    Note over C,Ev: FOR YOU FEED (two-tower retrieve -> rank -> serve)
    C->>Feed: GET /foryou?cursor
    Feed->>Rec: get candidates (user_id, context)

    Note over Rec,ANN: RETRIEVAL (millions -> hundreds)
    Rec->>Rec: lookup user embedding (two-tower user vector)
    Rec->>ANN: ANN search by cosine similarity
    ANN-->>Rec: ~1000 nearest video_ids
    Rec->>Rec: blend trending + follows + diversification
    Rec->>Rec: filter (already-seen, blocks, region eligibility)

    Note over Rec,Rank: RANKING (hundreds -> ~50)
    Rec->>Rank: score candidates (multi-task: watch_pct, like, share)
    alt ranker available
        Rank-->>Rec: top ~50 with scores
    else ranker degraded
        Note over Rec: fallback to per-user candidate cache + Following + Trending
        Rec-->>Rec: degraded list
    end

    Rec-->>Feed: ranked video_ids
    Feed->>DB: hydrate metadata + manifest URLs
    DB-->>Feed: video records
    Feed-->>C: ordered list (manifest URLs + prefetch hints)

    Note over C,Ev: PLAYBACK + PRELOAD
    C->>C: play video[0] from CDN
    par background preload
        C->>C: fetch manifest + first chunk for video[1..3]
    end

    Note over C,Ev: INTERACTION FEEDBACK (online learning)
    C-)Ev: POST /interaction (watch_pct, like, skip, share)
    Ev-)Rank: stream features for online training
    Ev-)Rec: refresh user embedding (hourly batch)
